Articles.Content:
GOTCHA!

The mod SnapDock made by Xiphos Aerospace is what broke it!

The whole thing is a cfg file that contains the following:

    @PART[*]:HAS[@MODULE[ModuleDockingNode]]:FINAL
    {@MODULE[ModuleDockingNode]{	captureMinRollDot = 0.98	snapRotation = true			snapOffset = 5}
    }

I guess these values shouldn't be tempered with next to your mod...
